Package: scRNAbassoon
Type: Package
Title: Optimized scRNA-seq Analysis Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-12-01
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dr. Eric Bareke", "Author", email = "eb.bioinfo@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Prof. Jacek Majewski", role = "ctb")
    )
Maintainer: Dr. Eric Bareke <eb.bioinfo@pm.me>
Description: An optimized Seurat v5 pipeline for comprehensive single-cell RNA-seq 
    analysis. Automates quality control, filtering, normalization, dimensionality 
    reduction, clustering, and cell type annotation. Includes integrated differential 
    expression analysis with Wilcoxon rank-sum testing, pathway enrichment via 
    over-representation analysis (ORA) and gene set enrichment analysis (GSEA), 
    and pseudotime trajectory inference using Slingshot. Designed for high-throughput 
    processing of 10X Genomics Cell Ranger outputs with customizable parameters and 
    publication-ready visualizations.
